<div class="p">
<sup>3</sup>Institut d´Investigacions Biomèdiques August Pi i Sunyer, August Pi i Sunyer Biomedical Research Institute, Barcelona, Spain</div>
<div class="p">
<sup>4</sup>Head Neck Clínic, Agència de Gestió d'Ajuts Universitaris i de Recerca, 2017-SGR-01581, Barcelona, Spain</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Avil%C3%A9s-Jurado%20FX"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Francesc Xavier Avilés-Jurado</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>2,</sup><sup>3,</sup><sup>4</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Prieto-Alhambra%20D"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Daniel Prieto-Alhambra</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Daniel Prieto-Alhambra</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, PhD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>5</sup>Centre for Statistics in Medicine, Nuffield Department of Orthopaedics, Rheumatology, and Musculoskeletal Sciences, University of Oxford, Oxford, UK</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Prieto-Alhambra%20D"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Daniel Prieto-Alhambra</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>5</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Gonz%C3%A1lez-S%C3%A1nchez%20N"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Nesly González-Sánchez</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
