</div>
</div>
<sup>1,</sup><sup>6</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="de%20Oss%C3%B3%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">José de Ossó</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3>
<span class="name western">José de Ossó</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
