<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="de%20Oss%C3%B3%20J"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">José de Ossó</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>1</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Arancibia%20C"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id5"><span class="name western">Claudio Arancibia</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id5">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Claudio Arancibia</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>1</sup>Otorhinolaryngology Head Neck Surgery Department, Institut Clínic d'Especialitats Mèdiques i Quirúrgiques, Hospital Clínic, Barcelona, Spain</div>
